 all the media persons and general public alike on this occasion of National Journalism Day, PM Prachanda has called for a conducive environment for broader cooperation with the media fraternity to address the concerns of the media sector.\n\nThe 8th National Journalism Day is being observed on Sunday by organizing different programs.\n\nThe government had decided to mark Baishakh 24 as National Journalism Day by coinciding with the first publication day of Gorkhapatra in the country.\n\nOn this occasion, two journalists would be honored with the title of Senior Journalist Award and six others with the national journalism prize.","title":"PM assures of broader consultations with stakeholders in making media laws","url":"http://english.khabarhub.com/2023/07/303009/","video":[]}
